{
  "title": "Xtra Silky Indian Milk Korma",
  "description": "A rich and creamy Rajasthani dish featuring semi-skimmed milk, this vegan-friendly korma is a perfect comfort food option. It is made with a variety of spices and poached to perfection.",
  "cuisine": "Indian",
